	<hint_static x="10" y="295" width="680" height="165">
		<text align="l" font="letterica16" r="180" g="180" b="180">
Hotkeys:
  ESC / Close      - close spawner
  Left / Right     - previous / next page
  Click category   - switch category
  Click item       - spawn

Spawn rules:
  Items (weapons, ammo, meds, artefacts) go to your inventory.
  Ammo/grenades spawn in batches (count shown on the button).
  Mutants and NPCs are spawned in world (toggle Target/Cluster below).

Toggles (world spawn only):
  Target: Actor  - spawn ~8m random offset from actor.
  Target: Aim    - spawn at point where your crosshair/look ~25m.
  Cluster: 1x    - one entity per click.
  Cluster: 3x/5x - burst (cluster around target, angle random).
		</text>
	</hint_static>

